            <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0cm; vertical-align: baseline;">① The Company will approve the use of services of the Member as long as the information entered during the registration process are true.</p>
            <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0cm; vertical-align: baseline;">② The Company reserves the right to reject the Member’s use of Services, or revoke the use of Services if they were approved previously, if one of the following pertains to the Member.</p>
            <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 25px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span lang="EN-US" style="border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;">1.&nbsp;</span>Violated a clause in the “Registration Procedure” article above</p>
            <p class="paragraph" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 25px; vertical-align: baseline;"><span lang="EN-US" style="border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;">2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="border: 1pt none windowtext; padding: 0cm;">Registered with the purpose of violating actions restricted by relevant laws</span></p>
