            <p class="MsoNormal" align="left" style="margin-bottom: 0cm; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: normal; vertical-align: baseline; ">② The Company's Privacy Policy does not apply to links to third-party services in the official website and each game services, excluding certain services provided separately.</p>
