            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <p>The company’s Privacy Policy is subject to change in accordance with the modifications made to the government’s relevant law or guideline, or to the regulation of the company. When a revision is made, it is disclosed on the official website. Therefore, users are recommended to look to the official website for any changes made to the policy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
